R2.6-2.2.0: May 17, 2017, Bruce Hill (bhill)
	Fixed a few remaining firefox help launchers to use areaDetectorHelp softlink to find documentation
	Updated ADCore edl screens w/ slac fonts and widgets and tweaked layouts.
	Added areaDetectorScreens/ prefix to each file reference and suffix .edl

R2.6-2.1.3: May 17, 2017, Hugo Slepicka (slepicka)
    Adding BitsPerPixel_RBV to ADApp/Db/NDArrayBase.template

R2.6-2.1.2:	May 16, 2017, Bruce Hill (bhill)
	Updated to asyn/R4.31-1.0.0

R2.6-2.1.1:	May 02, 2017, Bruce Hill (bhill)
	Updated to pvDatabaseCPP/R4.2.0-0.1.1

R2.6-2.1.0:	Apr 25, 2017, Bruce Hill (bhill)
	Enabled WITH_EPICS_V4 so we get NDPluginPva
	Provide macros defaults for overlay R,G,B colors
	Initialize SizeX and SizeY to 99999 so they clip to full image size.
	Also set EGU to sec for AcquireTime and AcquirePeriod pv's
	Modified whitespace on autosaveFields directives to match other R2-6 autosaveFields
	Added ArrayData.TSE field to autosave fields
	Added areaDetectorHelp and areaDetectorScreens soft links
	Added additional dummy pv's for CenterX and CenterY links
	Added additional status updates for NDFileWriteMessage and a TRACE_ERROR message
		for an attempt to start a capture from Single mode.
	Show paramName in writeInt32() trace msgs
	Set severity fields for ArrayCounter, ArrayRate, EnableCallbacks,
		BlockingCallbacks, and DroppedArrays to help new users to see
		potential issues w/ their plugins.
	Changed EnableCallbacks state names from Disable to Disabled, Enable to Enabled.
		Makes it more obvious to new users what the actual state of the callback is.
	Add dummy PV's as the defalt for Overlay Size links to avoid broken references to pv CP
	Applied bitsPerPixel.patch to bring in bitsPerPixel support from pcds-trunk
	Applied db-ADDR-TIMEOUT-defaults.patch to make ADDR default to 0 and TIMEOUT default to 1
    Removed unused dependecy of pvCommonCPP

R2.6-0.2.0:	Apr 5, 2017, Bruce Hill (bhill)
	Added WITH_HDF5 and other macros to enable additional plugins

R2.6-0.1.0:	Mar 24, 2017, Bruce Hill (bhill)
	Merged in updates from github R2-6
	Now depends on ADSupport instead of pkg_mgr for standard areaDetector plugins.

R2.2-0.1.0:	Oct 8, 2016, Bruce Hill (bhill)
	Updated to asyn R4.30-0.1.2
	Updated build files for git work-flow
	Includes asSupport.dbd instead of autosaveSupport.dbd for compatibility
		w/ SLAC autosave module

